{"tid":2405570,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯布少明：樓市見「牛氣」 樓價至少升5%","createTime":"2021-02-12T12:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T16:47:27.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d89bf8cb8be8933a89da9d9b2e960eab01b0be1","tid":2405570,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"美聯布少明：樓市見「牛氣」 樓價至少升5%<br />\n12:30 2021/02/12<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......展望牛年，布少明預計樓市將展現「牛氣」。事實上，農曆新年前本港樓市交投已經「陽春早現」。美聯物業房地產數據及研究中心綜合「一手住宅物業銷售資訊網」資料顯示，單計2月首9日已賣出逾600個新盤單位，相信全月一手銷售量有望錄逾1,200伙。新盤熱銷帶動市場氣氛，二手交投亦有望錄逾4,000宗......<br />\n<br />\n......樓價方面，如疫情隨鼠而遁，辛丑牛年的樓價可出現「小V型反彈」，升幅至少升5%，假如本港經濟強勁復甦，樓價甚至有力直撲2019年創出的歷史高位。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2877428/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%91%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%9A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E8%A6%8B%E3%80%8C%E7%89%9B%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D%20%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%8D%875%25?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2877428%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2598%258E%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%25A6%258B%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2589%259B%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%258D%25875%2525%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=5dbc1af2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2877428/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%91%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%9A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E8%A6%8B%E3%80%8C%E7%89%9B%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D%20%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%8D%875%25?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">牛年樓價至少升5%已是極度保守的估計</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cab1b714761f252beb3fba2ebc146bc0da351e90","tid":2405570,"uid":37688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"依條友日日都係hket出文唱好咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\